    "Id": "chassisdef_fire_scorpion_FSCR-3",
    "Name": "Fire Scorpion",
    "Details": "This Jihad variant of the Fire Scorpion, introduced 3071, has dropped equipment in favor of adding Jump Jets to the 'Mech. Designed for the role of close-quarters fighting and urban combat, this variant drops its LRM Launchers & A-Pods. In its place the 'Mech has been fitted with four torso mounted AP Gauss Rifles with 2 tons of ammunition. A single Jump Jet has been added in each of the 'Mech's leg actuators.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Cowl</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.13</color></b>",
